One of the reason why that I chose to major in Management Information Systems is because of various opportunities in the field of technology and business.
In the digital ade, I thought that MIS will be helpful to keep me updated on the latest technological advancements and trends. This ensures that I can be well-prepared to leverage emerging technologies for business innovation.
